text: Odontocerum is a genus of mortarjoint casemakers in the family Odontoceridae. There are at least three described species in Odontocerum. ==Species== * Odontocerum albicorne (Scopoli, 1763) * Odontocerum hellenicum Malicky, 1972 * Odontocerum lusitanicum Malicky, 1975 ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * Category:Trichoptera
title: Odontocerum
